import React from 'react' import { Link } from 'react-router-dom' import './Card.css' const Card = ({item}) => { const src1=item.attributes.data.img.attributes.url; const src2=item.attributes.data.img2.attributes.url; return (
e.target.src=src2} onMouseLeave={(e)=>e.target.src=src1}/>

{item.attributes.title}

${item.attributes.price} ${item.price}
) } export default Card
